abstract: National Assn of Realtors says its seasonally adjusted pending home sales index fell 1.8 percent in June to 110.3.
lead_paragraph: The National Association of Realtors said its pending home sales index fell 1.8 percent in June, though it was up 8.2 percent for the past 12 months.

headline.main: Limited Supply of Homes Held Back Sales in June
